title: Proposal to Boost the DVI-BNB farm and a New Syrup Pool
body:
#### PancakeSwap Welcomes Back Dvision Network ($DVI) to Syrup Pool!

CAKE holders, today we are happy to be able to offer you a new Syrup Pool from **Dvision Network**,  a new VR content ecosystem that is based on blockchain technology. 

#### What is Boost?

Boost is basically an increase in farm multiplier over a set period of time, which is offered in exchange for additional tokens from the boosted project, which are then put into a new Syrup Pool!

So basically, the DVI-BNB farm will go to a 1x multiple for 48 hours, then 0.5x thereafter. Don’t worry, this will only cause temporary dilution among the other farms. At the same time, there will be a new DVI Syrup Pool with 217,400 DVI tokens to be earned by staking CAKE.

#### The Syrup Pool:

Stake CAKE tokens to earn DVI tokens!

- **Total Tokens:** 217,400 DVI
- **Distribution duration:** 30 days
- **Start time:** Approx. 11am UTC on November 12th 2021
- **Finish time:** Approx. 11am UTC on December 12th 2021
- **Token rewards per block:** 0.2516 DVI

#### Max Stake per wallet:

100 CAKE for the first 48 hours, then unlimited CAKE staking afterwards.

To give as many CAKE holders the opportunity to Farm some Syrup pool rewards at a high APY, we will have a 100 CAKE token cap staking limit per user for the first 48 hours.

#### What is Dvision Network?

From the team: “Dvision Network is a multichain metaverse platform, built on top of the Ethereum Network and Binance Smart Chain. The web-based real-time network is powered by the DVI utility and governance token across its platform pillars of Meta-City, Meta-Space, and NFT Market: 

- Meta-City (Collection of Meta-Spaces) - A space where users can enjoy the metaverse, interact with other users, and engage in different events and activities such as fairs and games.
- Meta-Space (Tailored Virtual Estate) - A place where users can acquire and customize their personal land in order to establish and offer their own content within their virtual estate. 
- NFT Market (Marketplace) - A place where users can create and trade unique items.

Users are rewarded as they progress through the game, and contribute to the Dvision ecosystem's growth by participating in its NFT economy as creators and traders.”

#### To learn more about Dvision Network, the chefs advise you to visit their official communication channels:

- **Website:** https://dvision.network/
- **Twitter:** https://twitter.com/Dvision_network
- **Telegram:** https://t.me/dvisionnetworkglobal
- **Medium:** https://dvision-network.medium.com/

#### How do you stake CAKE to earn DVI rewards?
Follow this guide to staking in Syrup Pools: 

**[https://docs.pancakeswap.finance/products/syrup-pool/syrup-pool-guide](https://docs.pancakeswap.finance/products/syrup-pool/syrup-pool-guide)**

#### BEWARE OF FOOD POISONING! ⚠️⚠️⚠️💀

The official DVI token contract address on Binance Smart Chain is:  

[**https://www.bscscan.com/token/0x758fb037a375f17c7e195cc634d77da4f554255b**](https://www.bscscan.com/token/0x758fb037a375f17c7e195cc634d77da4f554255b)

Any other DVI token will be a scam and will result in a financial loss. Always verify the token address before purchasing tokens. If you receive a DVI token airdrop from another address, it’s probably a scam and we advise you to ignore them.
